1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:03,500
<i>Rain hammered the city
like it owed money.</i>

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,200
You're late, detective.

3
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:09,800
Traffic. And a body
on the Fifth Street bridge.

4
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:12,400
The same bridge as last month?

5
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:16,100
Same bridge, same caliber,
same note in the pocket.

6
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:18,300
{\an8}So we have a pattern.

7
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:21,900
We have a problem.
The mayor's office called twice.

8
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:24,100
Let them call a third time.

9
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:27,600
I don't chase headlines.
I chase the truth.

10
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,200
The truth doesn't pay
your pension, Reyes.

11
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:34,400
Neither does looking
the other way.

12
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:37,500
What did the note say this time?

13
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,000
One word, same as before:
<i>"Remember."</i>

14
00:00:41,400 --> 00:00:44,200
Remember what?
That's the question.

15
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:48,300
No. The question is
who wants us to forget.

16
00:00:48,700 --> 00:00:51,500
Get some sleep.
Tomorrow we visit the archive.

17
00:00:51,900 --> 00:00:55,000
The archive burned down
in '09, captain.

18
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:58,900
<i>Officially, it did.
Officially.</i>
